    <title class="- topic/title "><ph class="- topic/ph topic/title-wrapper ">3.2.2 标签基本功能</ph></title>
    <shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc ">如何不显示、删除和禁用自动标签，以及为文献添加标签。</shortdesc>
    <taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody ">
        <context class="- topic/section task/context ">
            <p class="- topic/p "/>
        </context>
        <steps class="- topic/ol task/steps ">
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">不显示自动标签</cmd>
                <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info ">
                    <p class="- topic/p ">当 Zotero 导入文献时，自动标签功能会将关键词和主题导入为标签，可能导致标签区域杂乱。以下是不显示自动标签的方法：</p>
                </info>
                <substeps class="- topic/ol task/substeps ">
                    <substep class="- topic/li task/substep ">
                        <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">如下图所示，点击左下角漏斗图标打开标签管理区域。</cmd>
                    </substep>
                    <substep class="- topic/li task/substep ">
                        <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">如下图所示，取消勾选"显示自动标签"。  <image class="- topic/image " href="file:/Users/mac/Desktop/2024入学/课程/技术写作/期末作业/小组作业/Zotero%20tutorial期末1.0/我自己的测试版/Chapter3的副本/part6/6-image/1使自动标签不显示或删除自动标签.png" id="image_zrz_n2c_ydc" placement="inline" width="300"/></cmd>
                    </substep>
                </substeps>
            </step>
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">删除现有自动标签</cmd>
                <substeps class="- topic/ol task/substeps " id="substeps_mrx_nwd_ldc">
                    <substep class="- topic/li task/substep ">
                        <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">如下图左上角"第一步"所示，点击"我的文库"。</cmd>
                    </substep>
                    <substep class="- topic/li task/substep ">
                        <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">如下图左下角"第二步所示"，点击漏斗图标。</cmd>
                    </substep>
                    <substep class="- topic/li task/substep ">
                        <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">如下图左下角"第三步"所示，勾选"删除此文献库中的自动标签"。 <image class="- topic/image " href="file:/Users/mac/Desktop/2024入学/课程/技术写作/期末作业/小组作业/Zotero%20tutorial期末1.0/我自己的测试版/Chapter3的副本/part6/6-image/2%20新确认删除自动标签.png" id="image_aqn_lfc_ydc" placement="inline" width="300"/>
                        </cmd>
                    </substep>
                    <substep class="- topic/li task/substep ">
                        <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">如下图所示，点击"ok"，删除现有自动标签。           <image class="- topic/image " href="file:/Users/mac/Desktop/2024入学/课程/技术写作/期末作业/小组作业/Zotero%20tutorial期末1.0/我自己的测试版/Chapter3的副本/part6/6-image/2确认删除自动标签.png" id="image_hr2_5dc_ydc" placement="inline" width="300"/></cmd>
                    </substep>
                </substeps>
            </step>
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">禁用自动标签</cmd>
                <substeps class="- topic/ol task/substeps " id="substeps_etb_2xd_ldc">
                    <substep class="- topic/li task/substep ">
                        <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">点击菜单栏"Zotero"</cmd>
                    </substep>
                    <substep class="- topic/li task/substep ">
                        <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">点击"设置"</cmd>
                    </substep>
                    <substep class="- topic/li task/substep ">
                        <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">点击"常规"</cmd>
                    </substep>
                    <substep class="- topic/li task/substep ">
                        <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">在"基于关键词和主题词自动为条目添加标签"前面方框内点击，使他处于不选中状态。
                                <image class="- topic/image " href="file:/Users/mac/Desktop/2024入学/课程/技术写作/期末作业/小组作业/Zotero%20tutorial期末1.0/我自己的测试版/Chapter3的副本/part6/6-image/3%20导入文献不自动导入关键词作为标签.png" id="image_rt4_kzd_ldc" placement="inline" width="300"/></cmd>
                    </substep>
                </substeps>
            </step>
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">为文献添加新标签</cmd>
                <substeps class="- topic/ol task/substeps " id="substeps_ngk_vwd_ldc">
                    <substep class="- topic/li task/substep ">
                        <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">如下图中上侧"第一步"所示，选中一篇文献。</cmd>
                    </substep>
                    <substep class="- topic/li task/substep ">
                        <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">如下图右侧"第二步"所示，点击标签图标。</cmd>
                    </substep>
                    <substep class="- topic/li task/substep ">
                        <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">如下图右上角"第三步"所示，点击加号图标。</cmd>
                    </substep>
                    <substep class="- topic/li task/substep ">
                        <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">如下图右侧"第四步"所示，在文本框里输入要新添加的标签名称，按回车键完成。
                                <image class="- topic/image " href="file:/Users/mac/Desktop/2024入学/课程/技术写作/期末作业/小组作业/Zotero%20tutorial期末1.0/我自己的测试版/Chapter3的副本/part6/6-image/4%20新给一篇文献添加标签.png" id="image_bmy_zfc_ydc" placement="inline" width="300"/></cmd>
                    </substep>
                </substeps>
            </step>
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">为多篇文献添加现有标签</cmd>
                <substeps class="- topic/ol task/substeps " id="substeps_x1k_jyd_ldc">
                    <substep class="- topic/li task/substep ">
                        <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">如下图"第一步"所示，选中多篇文献。</cmd>
                    </substep>
                    <substep class="- topic/li task/substep ">
                        <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">如下图"第二步"所示，将选中的多篇文献拖动到左下角的标签区域内选中的现有标签处。
                                <image class="- topic/image " href="file:/Users/mac/Desktop/2024入学/课程/技术写作/期末作业/小组作业/Zotero%20tutorial期末1.0/我自己的测试版/Chapter3的副本/part6/6-image/8%20为多篇文献添加现有标签.png" id="image_qpj_w2c_ydc" placement="inline" width="300"/></cmd>
                    </substep>
                </substeps>
            </step>
        </steps>
    </taskbody>
